Language: en

00:00:08.690 --> 00:00:12.780
To do a vertical jump through, you're going
to start in your hand roll.

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:13.990
With your thumb out.

00:00:13.990 --> 00:00:15.240
Your palm facing forward.

00:00:15.240 --> 00:00:20.370
The hoop is rotating forward on the right
side of my body.

00:00:20.370 --> 00:00:22.260
Palm is forward.

00:00:22.260 --> 00:00:26.400
Then, notice when the hoop touches your palm.

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:29.540
When it touches your palm you're going to
grab the hoop.

00:00:29.540 --> 00:00:34.750
You're going to cross, continue the rotation
and cross the hoop over on the left side of

00:00:34.750 --> 00:00:36.180
your body.

00:00:36.180 --> 00:00:41.760
And when your hoop is on the left side of
your body, you're going to step through one

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:44.210
foot at a time.

00:00:44.210 --> 00:00:50.969
And then keep the hoop vertical as you lift
it up over your head and then push it forward

00:00:50.969 --> 00:00:52.579
to continue your hand roll.

00:00:52.579 --> 00:00:54.120
So, one more time.

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:56.359
Breaking that down slowly.

00:00:56.359 --> 00:00:57.789
Grab.

00:00:57.789 --> 00:00:59.699
Cross to the left side.

00:00:59.699 --> 00:01:02.679
Step through with your left foot first.

00:01:02.679 --> 00:01:08.180
Keep the hoop vertical as it comes over your
head and continue your hand roll.

00:01:08.180 --> 00:01:11.979
A little bit faster.

00:01:11.979 --> 00:01:12.979
Grab.

00:01:12.979 --> 00:01:13.979
Cross.

00:01:13.979 --> 00:01:15.780
Step through.

00:01:15.780 --> 00:01:17.680
Hand roll.

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:18.680
Faster.

00:01:18.680 --> 00:01:31.060
Then when we get this going faster, it looks
really nice.

00:01:31.060 --> 00:01:37.030
So I'll do this facing the other way just
to show you what my left side is doing.

00:01:37.030 --> 00:01:38.080
Palm.

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:39.140
Palm.

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:40.200
Grab.

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:50.470
Cross step through and hand roll.

00:01:50.470 --> 00:01:55.450
And that's how you do a vertical jump through.

